<span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb290991b620e1fd91ee567345ee5ccd709d122b","tid":1544612,"uid":85965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:43:38.000Z","msg":"「但是我想很自豪的說我是一個普通的<span style=\"color: red;\">警務工作者</span>，和支持警察支持正義的市民」<br />\n<br />\n姐係警犬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1025f9d7ea6f0d22ea89c64a240dc3900d784604","tid":1544612,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:44:48.000Z","msg":"得架啦<br />\n留返同美國佬講啦"},{"pid":"5ca596fe70ca9df2c16f5d3e63e9185a6081ea26","tid":1544612,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:45:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5afcd753e9d561d6d162b1a2b14a9a710cbc230","tid":1544612,"uid":286670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:51:02.000Z","msg":"push reported"},{"pid":"aefcccf4f187ed63a20cdab5db65e660d4b7ba99","tid":1544612,"uid":75440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:41:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DvBPjn2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDvBPjn2.png&h=5b4d09b1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXv1auJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXv1auJ.png&h=f6fbf289&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MekTL23.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMekTL23.png&h=d3186f65&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V3cGauK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV3cGauK.png&h=1d0038f7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FwS3oPL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFwS3oPL.png&h=803e1695&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"ht